  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will You Wheel? is an early access car life simulation where you rebuild rusty cars into a race car, and hit the open road to prove it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FIX IT TO START.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make the car run again, then keep it in good condition and upgrade it over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/b155e94fa7172fc35f25d30f9d2a1de5.poster.avif?t=1771714707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/b155e94fa7172fc35f25d30f9d2a1de5.webm?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/b155e94fa7172fc35f25d30f9d2a1de5.mp4?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE THE BUILD. EARN CASH. UPGRADE WITH PARTS.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop the car to match changing goals as the build progresses: parts can be added or replaced, and the setup can be modified over time. Fund each step by selling parts to customers and ordering new components, turning a worn out project into a competitive race car.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TOW, HAUL, AND FIND PROJECTS.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a truck to transport parts and tow scrapyard vehicles out of the junkyard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/eceaa1bb632be5ca224f2a411fae6258.poster.avif?t=1771714707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/eceaa1bb632be5ca224f2a411fae6258.webm?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/eceaa1bb632be5ca224f2a411fae6258.mp4?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OPEN MAP. ENDLESS WAYS TO RACE.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive across a large open map, then enter different race events as your car improves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/a890508c40f46fea97bc9c490da19024.poster.avif?t=1771714707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/a890508c40f46fea97bc9c490da19024.webm?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/a890508c40f46fea97bc9c490da19024.mp4?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WIN THE RACE. CLAIM THE CAR.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win races to climb the blacklist. Each victory adds a new reward: the defeated driver’s car becomes part of the garage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Semi Detailed  car assembly with lots of parts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy junk cars, diagnose issues, repair, upgrade, and race</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order parts, build at home</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missions that keep the project cars funded</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple race types: drag, drift, street, rally</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open-world roads with traffic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Property purchases: houses, garages, shops</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will You Wheel? is an early access car life simulation where you rebuild rusty cars into a race car, and hit the open road to prove it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FIX IT TO START.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make the car run again, then keep it in good condition and upgrade it over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/b155e94fa7172fc35f25d30f9d2a1de5.poster.avif?t=1771714707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/b155e94fa7172fc35f25d30f9d2a1de5.webm?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/b155e94fa7172fc35f25d30f9d2a1de5.mp4?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE THE BUILD. EARN CASH. UPGRADE WITH PARTS.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Develop the car to match changing goals as the build progresses: parts can be added or replaced, and the setup can be modified over time. Fund each step by selling parts to customers and ordering new components, turning a worn out project into a competitive race car.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TOW, HAUL, AND FIND PROJECTS.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a truck to transport parts and tow scrapyard vehicles out of the junkyard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/eceaa1bb632be5ca224f2a411fae6258.poster.avif?t=1771714707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/eceaa1bb632be5ca224f2a411fae6258.webm?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/eceaa1bb632be5ca224f2a411fae6258.mp4?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OPEN MAP. ENDLESS WAYS TO RACE.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive across a large open map, then enter different race events as your car improves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/a890508c40f46fea97bc9c490da19024.poster.avif?t=1771714707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/a890508c40f46fea97bc9c490da19024.webm?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443770/extras/a890508c40f46fea97bc9c490da19024.mp4?t=1771714707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WIN THE RACE. CLAIM THE CAR.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win races to climb the blacklist. Each victory adds a new reward: the defeated driver’s car becomes part of the garage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Semi Detailed  car assembly with lots of parts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy junk cars, diagnose issues, repair, upgrade, and race</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order parts, build at home</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missions that keep the project cars funded</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple race types: drag, drift, street, rally</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open-world roads with traffic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Property purchases: houses, garages, shops</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
